Subtask 9: Set card spacing (margin-bottom: 12-16px)

Task 1.2.4: Populate Notification Content

Subtask 1: Add "New Email from PMO Director" notification (HIGH priority, email icon, 2h ago)

Description: "Review of Q4 data quality metrics requested"


Subtask 2: Add "DQ Assessment Due Soon" notification (HIGH priority, chart icon, 1d ago, with left highlight)

Description: "PMO Data Quality Assessment due in 7 days"


Subtask 3: Add "Workstream Progress Update" notification (MEDIUM priority, bell icon, 3d ago)

Description: "Data Strategy Document reached 30% completion"


Subtask 4: Add additional notifications as needed
Subtask 5: Ensure proper icon selection for each notification type

Task 1.2.5: Implement Notification Functionality

Subtask 1: Create click handler for individual notifications
Subtask 2: Implement "Clear All" functionality
