Section title with target icon
Three workstream cards in horizontal layout
Each card shows: title, description, progress bar, due date, tasks remaining, status badge


"AI Agent Context" section shows:

Section title with agent icon
Current workstream info
Current task info
Last interaction timestamp
"Continue Working" button


"Quick Actions" section shows:

Section title with lightning icon
Four action buttons in 2x2 grid
Each button with icon and label



Main Flow:

User scrolls to bottom of dashboard
User sees all four sections
User can view notification previews
User can click notifications to view full center
User can see active workstream status
User can see current AI context
User can continue working from context
User can access quick actions

Alternative Flow:

If no active workstreams, show empty state
If no AI context, show prompt to start
If notifications empty, hide preview section

