Summary of Major Missing Components:

Dashboard Main View: Complete notifications panel (left side) and upcoming assessments panel (right side) are entirely missing from implementation
Profile Settings Page: The comprehensive profile page with statistics cards and account details is not present in current implementation
AI Agent Chat Interface: The detailed chat interface with context awareness, section display, and suggested actions is missing
Notifications Center Modal: Full-featured notifications center with filtering and detailed notification cards is not implemented
Bottom Dashboard Panel: Active workstreams display, AI agent context section, and quick actions panel are absent

All these components need to be built from scratch to match the design specifications